tafsir[19]{c,v,t}:
  87,1,"Senin Innde joom ma gonɗo dow tagu Makko, ngowla Innde Makko mawninaa Mbo."
  87,2,"Oon takɗo aade hombo foti, hombo fooccii darnde."
  87,3,"Oon koddiranɗo tagooje leƴƴi mum e noone mum e sifaaji mum, O feewni kala ko taga e ko yaadi e mum."
  87,4,"Oon yaltinɗo e leydi durngol daabeeje mon."
  87,5,"O watti ngol yoorngol guuringol e ɓaleeri caggal nde ngol woni keccol."
  87,6,"Ma Min janngin Ma-aan nelaado- quraana, Min ndenndina mbo e ɓernde Ma A yejjittaa mbo abadan, woto adandir e jibriil e janngude mbo hono no mbaɗratnaɗa ko adii ngam reerɗude waasde yejjitde."
  87,7,"Si wonah ko Alla faala yo A yejjit ngam ñeeñal, Alla ceniiɗo O na anndi ko ɓanngi e ko wirnii hay ndiga wirnataako Mbo e ɗuum."
  87,8,"Min newnan Ma golle belooje Alla naatnooje aljanna."
  87,9,"Waaja aade en ko Min mbahyi Ma e quraana, siftinir ɓe ɗo waaju nafata."
  87,10,"Ma waacta e waaju Ma oon kulɗo Alla, sabu ko oon naftorto waaju."
  87,11,"Na woɗɗito waaju o, o doga mbo oon keefeero, sabu ko kanko ɓuri hiiteede ka laakara ngam naatde mbo yiite."
  87,12,"Oon naatoowo yiite mannge nge o tampa e nguleeki henge haa pooma."
  87,13,"Refti o saasnee e yiite o maayatah o foofto e lepte, o wuuratah nguurndam mbelɗam tedduɗam."
  87,14,"Malaama oon laaɓɗo e sirku e goopi."
  87,15,"O jantii ko sariyina e jikru, o tottiri juulde e mbaadi yamiraandi ndi."
  87,16,"Kono hoɗon ngardina nguurndam aduna e dow nguurndal laakira wondude noɗe mba*i seertude nih."
  87,17,"Na woodani laakara ɓural e dow aduna sabu ko woni ko laakara e dakkamme duumiiɗo e neema mbo taƴandirtah haa pooma."
  87,18,"Ko Min haalani on ko e jamirooje e kabaruuji ina e ɗereeji gadiiɗi tellaade ko adii."
  87,19,"ɗiin ngoni tellinaaɗi e Ibraahiima e Muusa yo kisal won e mum en."
